呢招算唔算高就唔太清楚,<br />\n但至少就比林太高先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:43:35.000Z","msg":"如果比陳同佳自己坐機去台灣<br />\n台灣又話受落地簽證<br />\n到時台灣可以點應對？<br />\n人又要收 證據又無"},{"pid":"08277b72fe9d2fc7f3edd7e4fa59357909234c81","tid":1670503,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"沒有xx, 只有xx<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fcc738bb1d6610e106518ccbdb9bbe37fac920","tid":1670503,"uid":46746,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:47:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭條廢柴點會夠人玩政治 讀死書佢就叻 潛水潛到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f8d7bbd3d985d66d1a794353e5564a91e2ca88","tid":1670503,"uid":277572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:47:28.000Z","msg":"佢應該講埋唔會保證一定唔判死刑，嚇到隻陳同佳唔投案又會係一場好戲"},{"pid":"7544da9e4a02e392989feefb962f34d8fd6928c9","tid":1670503,"uid":4329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08277b72fe9d2fc7f3edd7e4fa59357909234c81","tid":1670503,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"沒有xx, 只有xx<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:48:42.000Z","msg":"唔怪得熟口熟面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d05a119469b1753407798cb9eee67a31fc24ec","tid":1670503,"uid":171788,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"738824ee5d687d35893338a7363f7a18b37589c0","tid":1670503,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":89,"score":-88,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T21:09:10.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌收皮啦<br />\n撞正香港依家內亂就鳩up 抽水拉選票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:48:56.0